text: Graham Numa (born 19 August 1954) is a Papuan windsurfer. He competed in the 1988 Summer Olympics and the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== == External links == * * Category:1954 births Category:Living people Category:Sailors at the 1988 Summer Olympics – Division II Category:Sailors at the 1992 Summer Olympics – Lechner A-390 Category:Olympic sailors of Papua New Guinea Category:Papua New Guinean male sailors (sport) Category:Papua New Guinean windsurfers
